Clustre: intro-optional-goodies:
At the end of the Q&A section, you will exit D-Well. Optionally, you can look att the bespoke recommendations report and knowledge graph that D-Well generates.

You can also opt-in to get a copy of the report by email from Onepoint.
Clustre: intro-nutshell:
From the main D-Well screen, select an area of interest from the set of starter options provided - or type in your own response.

D-Well will ask follow-up questions to further clarify your input, in the familiar conversational format of a GenAI assistant.
